_sText: +-------------------------------+ | fy_simpsons_kniferush | +-------------------------------+ __________________ I don't have the simpsons textures, so i used standard textures. Gameplay Synopsis: Each player gets one random weapon with deagle and knife. If you rush over the bridge, your weapons will be dropped. You can use your knife to kill people on the other side. Max players : 24 __________________ have fun! -fetter Hagrid (vince.)
